That all said, it is pretty much mandatory these days to have an authenticator for any online game. As much as I hate the bloody little things, it is just like not updating your computer with security patches running without one. You are just begging to get hosed over. I have used ones for years with FFXI, use one with FFXIV, SC2 and pretty much every game that offers it. I am unsure about the smart phone apps yet, still questionable.</div>
